===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{l|en|The [[finger]] between the [[forefinger]] and the [[ring finger]]}}; this is the longest finger.
# An {{l|en|obscene}} gesture directed towards another as an insult: a literal or sometimes figurative raising of the middle finger at someone.
#* '''2007''', Dominique Paul, ''The Possibility of Fireflies‎'', page 62:
#*: Her whole way of being is a big '''middle finger''' to the other guy.

